0.title: Rules
0.body:
How to use this mod:
Choose a Role card and Race. Optionally, include a Trait and/or Aspect. 
Select the cards you've chosen. Select Save Object. 
Load your chosen Hexplore It volume, open Objects > Saved Objects and drag your saved cards into the mod.
Alternatively, Additively Load this mod in the volume mod.

If you want to use Roles specific to a given volume, check the symbols. Current symbols are:
Crowned skull: Valley of the Dead King
Golem head: Forests of Adrimon
Ring of teeth: Sands of Shurax
